Kardex Investor Agosti Wants Merger With Swisslog, F&W Reports

-- B y   S i m o n e   M e i e r
-- 
2011-08-13T10:48:29Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-13/kardex-investor-agosti-wants-merger-with-swisslog-f-w-reports.html
Adriano Agosti, who has been
building his stake in  Kardex AG (KARN) , proposed that the company scrap
plans for a capital increase and instead merge with  Swisslog
Holding AG (SLOG) ,  Finanz und Wirtschaft  reported, citing a letter to
the board it obtained.  Agosti, chairman of GoldenPeaks Capital, increased his
holding of Kardex over the past weeks but remained below 3
percent, the newspaper said. He owns more than 5 percent of
Swisslog.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Simone Meier in Zurich at 
 smeier@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
